<p>My question is that given that I would follow the 10% discharge cycle would that not cause the battery to &#8216;fail&#8217; sooner since discharging 10% and then charging to 100% 4,700 times would roughly equate to 470 100% discharges? I&#8217;m sure I may be misunderstanding something, but I don&#8217;t see how the numbers add up.</p></div>
