				<div class="commentAuthor"><strong>Guillaume</strong> wrote:</div>
				<div class="commentBody"><p>@Sandeep</p>

<p>If you intend to use your laptop charged in for an extended period of time, remove the battery from it at 40% capacity.</p>

<p>You should not keep the battery on the laptop. The laptop will keep charging the battery as soon as it losses a little capacity and will eventually reduce the battery life expectancy.</p></div>
