<p>You want to run the laptop without the battery if you can. Don&#8217;t leave the battery in the laptop when you are connected on the 120 Vca. A poor battery charger will reduce your battery life with an bad charging method.</p>

<p>As it was said earlier, the optimal charge level is around 50% of the battery capacity. You don&#8217;t want to go crazy with your laptop&#8217;s charge level. I suggest you to use the laptop between 40-100% of your battery capacity and then recharge it.</p></div>
