			<div class="articlePart" id="articlePart2">
			<h3 style="display:block" class="current">The Battery and You</h3>
				<div style="display:block">
					<ul id="nav_categories" class="nav_categories">
	<li>
						<h4>From Birth to Retirement</h4>
						
						<a href="http://batteryuniversity.com/learn/article/how_to_prime_batteries" >How to Prime Batteries</a>
						
						<a href="http://batteryuniversity.com/learn/article/how_to_store_batteries" >How to Store Batteries</a>
						
						<a href="http://batteryuniversity.com/learn/article/health_concerns" >Health Concerns with Batteries</a>
						
						<a href="http://batteryuniversity.com/learn/article/how_to_transport_batteries" >How to Transport Batteries</a>
						
						<a href="http://batteryuniversity.com/learn/article/recycling_batteries" >How to Recycle Batteries</a>
						
						<a href="http://batteryuniversity.com/learn/article/do_and_dont_battery_table" >Summary of Do&#8217;s and Don&#8217;ts</a>
						
					</li>
	<li>
						<h4>How to Prolong Battery Life</h4>
						
						<a href="http://batteryuniversity.com/learn/article/setting_performance_standards" >Setting Battery Performance Standards</a>
						
